PLACEHOLDER: interruption.mp3
Description: Brief audio cue for speaker interruptions in podcast-style conversations
Suggested content: Quick "whoosh" or subtle "click" sound (0.2-0.5 seconds)
Usage: Triggered by [SFX: interruption] cues in doc_theatre scripts
Recommended volume: -20dB to -16dB normalized
Format: MP3, 128kbps minimum
